<section class="about-hero">
    <div>
      <div class="label" style="margin-bottom:20px;">Our Story</div>
      <h1 class="about-h1 reveal">We didn't set out to build an agency.<br><span>We set out to fix something</span><br>broken.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="about-hero-body">
      <p class="reveal">OJ and Vartika spent years working closely with real startups — not the ones on magazine covers, the ones actually figuring it out. Through Ghar Ghar Entrepreneur, they interviewed founders, told their stories, and kept showing up at startup events in Bengaluru where the real conversations happen.</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d1">And one thing came up again and again: brilliant products, completely stuck at marketing</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d2">Founders spending everything on building and nothing left for bringing it to the world. No clear partner. No one to take it from idea to audience without five different vendors, five different briefs, and zero coordination"</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d2">So they became that partner</p>
      <p class="reveal reveal-d2">ScratchBox exists for brands that are done starting over with every new agency. We come in wherever you are — zero to launch, or stuck halfway — and we grow with you from there.</p>
      <div class="who-actions reveal reveal-d3">
        <a class="btn-lime" href="/contact/">Work with us <span class="arr">↗</span></a>
        <a class="btn-ghost" href="/services/">See services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

